sjm.parse.tokens
Class TokenAssembly

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--sjm.parse.Assembly
        |
        +--sjm.parse.tokens.TokenAssembly
public class TokenAssembly
extends Assembly

A TokenAssembly is an Assembly whose elements are Tokens. Tokens are, roughly, the chunks of text that a Tokenizer returns.
